Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gnhm2ns","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_start"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：初始化 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_list"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 对象。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-t1pigt2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-t1pigt2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-92wx4on","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-92wx4on","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_arg"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：从 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_list"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中获取下一个参数。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-jfn1sxv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-jfn1sxv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-moa6w59","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-moa6w59","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_end"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：清理 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"va_list"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 对象。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gn6mhr2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gn6mhr2","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"示例："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7cnkour","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockFenceOffset":2,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7cnkour","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \u003ccstdarg\u003e // 包含 C 风格可变参数宏的头文件\n#include \u003ciostream\u003e\n\n// 正确的 C 风格可变参数函数\nint sum_safe(int count, …) { // count 是固定参数，用于指示后续可变参数的数量\n    int s = 0;\n    va_list args; // 声明一个 va_list 对象\n    va_start(args, count); // 初始化 args，第二个参数是最后一个固定参数\n\n    for (int k = 0; k \u003c count; k++) {\n        // va_arg 从 args 中获取下一个参数，并指定其类型为 int\n        s += va_arg(args, int);\n    }\n\n    va_end(args); // 清理 args\n    return s;\n}\n\n// 示例调用\nint main() {\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Sum of 3 numbers: \" \u003c\u003c sum_safe(3, 10, 20, 30) \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出 60\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Sum of 5 numbers: \" \u003c\u003c sum_safe(5, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5) \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出 15\n    // 警告：如果 count 与实际传入的参数数量或类型不匹配，仍然可能导致未定义行为。\n    // 例如 sum_safe(3, 10, 20); // 传入参数不足\n    // 例如 sum_safe(3, 10, 20, \"hello\"); // 传入类型不匹配\n    return 0;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-sl8yxk6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sl8yxk6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.2 现代 C++ 的可变参数函数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-1be55hl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1be55hl","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C 风格的可变参数函数虽然灵活，但存在类型不安全、难以使用等缺点。现代 C++ (C++11 及更高版本) 提供了更安全、更强大、更类型安全的替代方案："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-jgoyjso","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-jgoyjso","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.2.1 可变参数模板"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-akmt78q","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-akmt78q","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-sc6uent","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-sc6uent","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-68aaq5u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-68aaq5u","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠template\u0026lt;typename… Args\u0026gt; void func(Args… args);"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7lar7cx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7lar7cx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-exgbtyz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-exgbtyz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特点："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 可以在编译时处理任意数量和任意类型的参数，具有完全的类型安全性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-7wy6emz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-7wy6emz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-l51jc0b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l51jc0b","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用途："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 实现 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::tuple"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::make_unique"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 等泛型功能。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-luyfuwu","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-luyfuwu","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"template\u003ctypename T\u003e\nT sum_modern(T t) {\n    return t;\n}\n\ntemplate\u003ctypename T, typename… Args\u003e\nT sum_modern(T first, Args… rest) {\n    return first + sum_modern(rest…);\n}\n\n// 示例调用\nint main() {\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Sum: \" \u003c\u003c sum_modern(1, 2, 3, 4, 5) \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出 15\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Sum: \" \u003c\u003c sum_modern(1.1, 2.2, 3.3) \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出 6.6\n    return 0;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-fa7qjh4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fa7qjh4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.2.2 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::initializer_list"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (C++11)"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mdce55j","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mdce55j","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-1zpsouc","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1zpsouc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-l94ydxc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l94ydxc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"⁠ReturnType functionName(std::initializer_list\u0026lt;Type\u0026gt; list);"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-967xiu4","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-967xiu4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-pbjqlt5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-pbjqlt5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特点："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 用于接受同类型参数的可变数量列表。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-w20ka6i","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-w20ka6i","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-2l7jhem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2l7jhem","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"用途："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 构造函数、函数参数，例如 ⁠"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"std::vector"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的构造函数。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-uy7hy5u","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uy7hy5u","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Qysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"#include \u003cinitializer_list\u003e\n\ndouble sum_list(std::initializer_list\u003cdouble\u003e list) {\n    double total = 0;\n    for (double val : list) {\n        total += val;\n    }\n    return total;\n}\n\n// 示例调用\nint main() {\n    std::cout \u003c\u003c \"Sum: \" \u003c\u003c sum_list({1.0, 2.0, 3.0, 4.0}) \u003c\u003c std::endl; // 输出 10.0\n    return 0;\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-az3pfwi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-az3pfwi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.1.2.3**函数重载"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-9v9a9ro","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-9v9a9ro","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于参数数量较少且固定的几种情况，可以直接通过重载函数来提供不同的版本。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-dhr19wn","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-dhr19wn","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.2 缺省参数"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hvtbe4q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hvtbe4q","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以在定义函数时为参数提供默认值。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"retuenType funcName(type arg1, type arg2, type arg3 = value3)"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 如果某个参数给了缺省值，其右边的参数都需要给参数值。"}]}]}